{"tid":1480450,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"未FC - 流傳明天中共會打壓（抗爭有望）","createTime":"2019-08-17T10:11:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-17T10:25:54.000Z","uid":196227,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"fcc1f5cb4b1695efc92bcb5cc42cff4676f1d104","tid":1480450,"uid":196227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T10:11:53.000Z","msg":"網上流傳信息（冇F.C.)<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n星期日盡量早點回家，<br />\n因應18號大型示威，<br />\n小心自身安全，<br />\n如果香港政府控制不到，就出動8萬武警，<br />\n中國政府已經失去耐性，鎮壓無可避免，<br />\n介時會宵禁數天，<br />\n<br />\n請買定一點食物在家，<br />\n如沒必要不要外出，<br />\n香港人請保重。<br />\n<br />\n一半入去佐敦，槍会山军營，另一半赤柱军營及石岗，佈放哂準備今晚及明晚泛民制造全港(大乱)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n想嚇尻我們<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n聽日照出，敵人越驚，我們就做到底<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n抗爭有望啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n善用不推文回覆，純粹想大家知道對家幾驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38224670128469298338faec17ea0f12dad921c4","tid":1480450,"uid":196227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T10:16:32.000Z","msg":"推818post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22ea62cd45002b0f578cda7fcfcdbd6a125968ea","tid":1480450,"uid":189679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T10:16:56.000Z","msg":"唔好咁無聊啦，未Fc講經咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b111f2be1e74d430f8f8784bff2e51ef77001bfc","tid":1480450,"uid":196227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T10:17:05.000Z","msg":"歡迎負評"},{"pid":"9db077330152b3108b7ad55b21ef58d18a29249d","tid":1480450,"uid":28970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T10:17:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />貼黎把撚 對家係就快啲出手啦"}